| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4935 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a75022a-6312-5e18-a1c9-02854ff4eb1a"
